sourcesContent: import './App.css'; import Title from "./Pages/home_page/Title"; import Login_page from "./Pages/login_display/login_page"; import NewPatientPage from "./Pages/new_patient/new_patient_detail_page"; import Admin_page from "./Pages/admin_page/admin_page"; function App() { const DUMMY_PATIENT = [{ first_name: 'Reece', middle_name: 'W', last_name: 'Colbus', birth_date: '02/08/1991', phone_number: '9099089703', email_address: 'rcolbus@me.com', street_address_line1: '857 e 25th', street_address_line2: '', city: 'Upland', state: 'CA', zip_code: '91784', photo_path: 'picture goes here', appointment_time: '16:30', appointment_date: '02/21/21' }, { first_name: 'Poot', middle_name: 'W', last_name: 'Colbus', birth_date: '02/08/1991', phone_number: '9099089703', email_address: 'rcolbus@me.com', street_address_line1: '857 e 25th', street_address_line2: '', city: 'Upland', state: 'CA', zip_code: '91784', photo_path: 'picture goes here', appointment_time: '16:30', appointment_date: '02/21/21' }] let component switch (window.location.pathname) { case '/': component = break case '/Login': component = <Login_page/> break case '/Register': component = <NewPatientPage/> break case '/Login/Admin': component = <Admin_page props={DUMMY_PATIENT}/> break } return ( <div> {component} </div> ) } export default App;
